text: Vatsavai is a village in the NTR district in the Indian state of Andhra Pradesh. It is part of Vatsavai mandal in Nandigama revenue division. According to the 2011 Census of India, the population of Vatsavai is about 9,554 people. The village has around 2,631 houses. == References == * * Category:Villages in Andhra Pradesh
